00:54:36,851 --> 00:54:37,391
moving into a...

929
00:54:38,111 --> 00:54:39,531
brand new partnership. Thank you.

930
00:54:40,412 --> 00:54:42,352
Yeah. I mean, I think I think most of

931
00:54:42,372 --> 00:54:44,493
the manifestations of these learnings are not

932
00:54:45,053 --> 00:54:47,034
they're not at the green light phase. They're not

933
00:54:47,074 --> 00:54:48,834
at the milestone phase. They're in the like

934
00:54:49,215 --> 00:54:51,255
the day to day decisions that

935
00:54:51,375 --> 00:54:53,396
everyone on your team is making culturally.

936
00:54:54,541 --> 00:54:59,406
And so we found that if we can make that transition internally in our organization,

