00:54:59,907 --> 00:55:02,210
then we feel really confident that we can make something great.

938
00:55:02,270 --> 00:55:06,795
We can convince anyone that it's going to be amazing,

939
00:55:06,855 --> 00:55:09,358
whether that's our players or our partners or our parents.

