00:57:12,494 --> 00:57:15,117
We've found that there are things in the game that we could release

972
00:57:15,817 --> 00:57:21,742
that might very briefly create some negative sentiment,

973
00:57:21,762 --> 00:57:23,224
but then that quickly rebounds as players,

974
00:57:23,244 --> 00:57:25,065
because sometimes players just don't like change,

975
00:57:25,085 --> 00:57:26,847
and then they understand the difference,

976
00:57:26,867 --> 00:57:28,889
but they might be really great for the overall health of the game.

977
00:57:28,969 --> 00:57:31,051
It causes people to show up more, to play more,

