00:57:44,843 --> 00:57:48,186
but if you don't know what the silent majority are thinking,

985
00:57:48,226 --> 00:57:49,927
if you don't know what's happening with engagement,

986
00:57:50,207 --> 00:57:52,229
you're probably making the wrong decisions.

987
00:57:52,389 --> 00:57:53,990
And so we try to make all of our leaders

988
00:57:54,791 --> 00:57:57,733
like see that full picture of what success is

989
00:57:57,813 --> 00:58:00,955
so that they can balance those different axes.

